  Locus:
    Page: 317
    Verse: 9
Tags:
  - Mind
---
If you give your mind your full, detached attention, you begin to
understand the futility of all mental activities. Watch the mind wandering
here and there, seeking out useless or unnecessary things or ideas which
will ultimately only create misery for itself.
